Package controller

Class PhotoController

java.lang.Object
controller.PhotoController
All Implemented Interfaces:
LogOutController
public class PhotoController extends Object implements LogOutController
This class is used to control the Photo List scene allowing the user to implement many methods with their Album.
Author:
Himani Patel, elizabeth lam
